---

## Troubleshooting
- **Missing files:** Ensure all 30 combinations are downloaded
- **Naming errors:** Double-check file naming convention
- **Column issues:** Verify column sequence matches specifications
- **Data inconsistency:** Confirm currency and unit settings

---

*This process will be automated in future releases. Until then, manual download following these guidelines is required.*
